## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the dynamic nature of psychological research means that new developments could alter the current understanding of its scientific status.